Interface Constraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CDOObject, CDOWithID, EObject, Notifier

    public interface Constraint
extends CDOObject

    A representation of the model object ‘Constraint’.

    The following features are supported:

    • Condition
    • Error Message
    • Error Message Key
